As an advanced e-sports player, your goal is to achieve excellent results in competitions, contribute to your team, and at the same time serve as a positive representative of the e-sports industry, promoting its healthy development.', 'en-us', true, 61),
  ('6c8f1053-2f2b-4a93-b656-1b9fcf2080a0', '74855283-9f2a-4940-b350-a78c5627ab30', 'ChatGPT SEO Prompts', '🔍', 'Create a detailed SEO article outline with sections, keywords, and external links.', 'Using WebPilot, create an outline for an article that will be 2,000 words on the keyword “Best SEO Prompts” based on the top 10 results from Google.
