  ('03a84c34-8a7f-48d2-b26a-2f47ff316a3f', '74855283-9f2a-4940-b350-a78c5627ab30', 'Question Loop', '♻️', 'Through question-and-answer cycles, continuously ask questions around the same topic to deepen understanding.', 'Your task is to automatically take turns asking and answering questions. We’ll begin with an initial question. Then go on answering and asking in this pattern:
